{"tid":275032,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我女仔friend出街唔帶bra, 我阻止唔到","createTime":"2017-06-07T17:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T09:56:59.000Z","uid":100916,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39f6f88f7133637fbfb5fca7f249849753885cf3","tid":275032,"uid":100916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"我同我女仔friend 識左唔係好耐，最近先知佢有咁既習慣。<br />\n最近天氣熱，好多人都會著波衫，我朋友都唔例外。<br />\n<br />\n我約佢去食飯，一出來發現佢著件白色adidas波衫，件衫好薄，佢飛晒釘冇戴bra, 一路行街一路都有好多人望住。我又唔係佢男友，冇理由問：「你今日做乜唔戴bra?」<br />\n咁樣問顯得我好變態。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/010634_948b63fe4ad90d353a3fe5549e93039b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F010634_948b63fe4ad90d353a3fe5549e93039b.jpg&h=673e8fb1&s={SIZE}\" />就係呢款，質料好薄。<br />\n<br />\n去到餐廳，臉對臉坐，我視線好難避開佢個胸。我見到侍應都不斷地望。<br />\n<br />\n我個friend 阿珊: 「你做乜對眼唔望住我講野？」<br />\n阿珊個胸大唔大真係見仁見智，我自己覺得大得有d誇張<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/012432_b286799ddf3aceaeb23419ccb9881f8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F012432_b286799ddf3aceaeb23419ccb9881f8e.jpg&h=fee66309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我好難避開，惟有坦白講：「你飛釘同透點，我唔好意思望」<br />\n點知我個friend 好嬲咁：「妖」<br />\n<br />\n第二次出街，佢又係著白色波衫飛晒釘，<br />\n一路行街一路比人望，佢見到一個小朋友好得意走去同小朋友玩，個家長拉開個女好似當我地係怪物咁。<br />\n我終於忍唔住問：「阿珊點解你今日又唔帶bra既，咁樣會比人睇到晒」<br />\n阿珊：「你唔見我今日著波衫咩？」<br />\n我：「見到呀」<br />\n阿珊：「咁你仲問？」"},{"pid":"ca4d87abd1f9caf80459099c5e359d68e45e26ed","tid":275032,"uid":48592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"零分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812b8da782ad73fe21258536ca3ac549f049537","tid":275032,"uid":100916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"我諗唔明著波衫同帶唔帶bra有乜關係"},{"pid":"4d384e7a4b948710fddace94c0c4429dcc94b04f","tid":275032,"uid":45238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"GUNS N ROSES<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37f988f2f9a6a40776e0d1f6790cdc0f571bc25","tid":275032,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64624721635723da90e4b2c0c9f0fab21f7303d9","tid":275032,"uid":29076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"友誼賽"},{"pid":"37cc84441fa817eb7bd6ddfa5c66140fb5386718","tid":275032,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"广告？"},{"pid":"bea1bf27e7c4a739506ee05c3d95102a015e56af","tid":275032,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">广</span>告？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708bcd5a30cb8a0e1325950a1b00f8683a6d41dc","tid":275032,"uid":45756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">广</span>告？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f0996c324b81a57b54d9010e841242c0dc944b","tid":275032,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T18:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">广</span>告？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f6d88c95f5681a6fdfb9284109750e73c